            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve" xml:lang="Latin">
                <ab>
                    <lb n="1"/><persName corresp="#maximianusiunior"><expan><abbr>Fl</abbr><ex>avio</ex></expan> Maximi<supplied reason="lost" evidence="previouseditor" corresp="#bertolini1874a #bertolini1874b">a</supplied>no</persName> fideli,
                    <lb n="2"/>filio ca<unclear>r</unclear>issimo,
                    <lb n="3"/><persName corresp="#maximianusmaior"><expan><abbr>Fl</abbr><ex>avius</ex></expan> Maximianus</persName> fidelis
                    <lb n="4"/>pater, arcam de pro
                    <lb n="5" break="no"/><w xml:id="w1">prio</w> <w xml:id="w2"><expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex cert="medium">uo</ex></expan></w> vivus <choice><reg>com</reg><orig>con</orig></choice>
                    <lb n="6" break="no"/>paravit et sibi<surplus>s</surplus>.
                </ab>
            </div>
            <div type="apparatus">
                <listApp>
                    <app loc="5" from="#w1" to="#w2">
                        <lem>
                            prio <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex cert="medium">uo</ex></expan>
                        </lem>
                        <rdg source="#bertolini1874a #bertolini1874b">
                            prio
                        </rdg>
                        <rdg>
                            prio<surplus>s</surplus>
                        </rdg>
                    </app>
                </listApp>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                <p>
                    To <persName corresp="#maximianusiunior" xml:lang="la">Flavius Maximianus</persName>, a loyal and most beloved son,  his faithful father <persName corresp="#maximianusmaior">Flavius Maximianus</persName> made this chest from his own means while still alive, and for himself.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div type="translation" xml:lang="it">
                <p>
                    A <persName ref="#maximianusiunior" xml:lang="la">Flavius Maximianu</persName>, fedele, figlio carissimo, <persName ref="#maximianusmaior" xml:lang="la">Flavius Maximianus</persName>, padre fedele, da vivo preparò a proprie spese il sarcofago per lui e per sé.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary" xml:lang="en">
                <p>
                    This inscription lacks the comminatory formula
                </p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary" xml:lang="it">
                <p>
                    Iscrizione priva della formula comminatoria.
                </p>
            </div>
